1
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:06,080
My thirty thousand soldiers of the Song Army...

2
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:08,940
actually died because of the Emperor's suspicion.

3
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:12,330
Then what was the point of them dying on the battlefield?

4
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,160
Father, Brother.

5
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:16,320
Did you see through this as well,

6
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,160
and choose to die willingly?

7
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,320
Rest assured.

8
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:22,280
I will find out the truth as soon as possible,

9
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:25,010
to comfort the spirits of the Song Army in heaven.

10
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,120
Huanghuacai.

11
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,330
Why are you here?

12
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:33,840
Don't worry. I will help you investigate the truth.

13
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,200
How?

14
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,600
One day,

15
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:39,580
I will make the person behind this pay the price.

16
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,400
Manchuan.

17
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,160
There is something I find very strange.

18
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,759
Why did Tuoya expose Shen Lingbo in front of me?

19
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,920
And don't you think it's too much of a coincidence?

20
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:50,120
Every time we get a step closer to the truth,

21
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,560
Tuoya gives us a push.

22
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,039
You mean she dragged Shen Lingbo into this on purpose?

23
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:57,240
Shen Lingbo might not be innocent,

24
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:59,720
but Tuoya wants to use us to get rid of her,

25
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,160
and test us at the same time.

26
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,600
She's asking for too much.

27
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,600
Then I'll go test Shen Lingbo again.

28
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:07,080
You're going to see her alone again?

29
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,960
Are you jealous?

30
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:10,840
No.

31
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,250
Don't worry.

32
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,660
I won't be that foolish again.

33
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,480
Shen Lingbo is a snake.

34
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,040
She makes no sound before she bites,

35
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,000
and she doesn't let go once she bites.

36
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,130
I'm worried she'll swallow you whole.

37
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,440
But isn't the hunter here?

38
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:30,480
Come with me to a place tomorrow.

39
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:30,920
Where?

40
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,560
To investigate the case.

41
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,000
Huanghuacai.

42
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,079
The traces here are very clear.

43
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,760
It shows the bodies weren't moved here

44
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,760
after they were killed.

45
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:04,320
So those children from the Academy were killed right here.

46
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,880
Let's sort this out.

47
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,480
The Academy has always been strictly managed.

48
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:11,010
Even the parents can't enter or leave freely.

49
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,160
So how did those children

50
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:15,440
get from the Academy to here?

51
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,320
This is the first suspicious point.

52
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,480
Second, since the incident,

53
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,980
I looked up all kinds of beast claw marks.

54
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:26,650
The marks here don't look like they were made by wild beasts.

55
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,400
That's what puzzles me too.

56
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,000
Whether it's the marks on the ground

57
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:32,360
or on the trees,

58
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,000
they are all too suspicious.

59
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,240
So we can conclude,

60
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,680
it was done by humans.

61
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:41,240
Those children from the Academy

62
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,700
were either rich or noble.

63
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:45,040
What was the killer's motive?

64
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:48,720
I know of a soul-stealing secret technique on the grassland.

65
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,200
Huanghuacai, let's go back.

66
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,040
We can't find anything here anyway.

67
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,570
Indeed, there are no clues.

68
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,320
Let's go.

69
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:57,610
Let's go.

70
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,640
Do I need to take care of it?

71
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,300
Do you want to alert the enemy?

72
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,320
But if we do nothing,

73
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,440
and let them keep investigating,

74
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,680
we'll be exposed sooner or later.

75
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:20,200
Then let Bai Chuyi sink deeper into the trap.

76
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:23,520
By then, even if she risks her life to prove something,

77
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,080
no one will believe her.

78
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,520
Chuyi, eat more meat.

79
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,570
Don't just drink the porridge.

80
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,040
Chuyi, are you afraid?

81
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:03,320
The cases at the Academy are indeed bizarre.

82
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,880
Anyone would be scared.

83
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:10,200
Don't overthink it. Your sister-in-law is already investigating.

84
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,440
Okay.

85
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,420
The Heir of Prince Duan and Princess Tuoya are here.

86
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,320
Why are they here?

87
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,490
What are you doing here?

88
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,960
I am here on His Majesty's orders to investigate a case.

89
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,020
Where is Bai Chuyi?

90
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,360
We need to ask her a few questions.

91
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,820
Are you blind? Can't you see a child this big?

92
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:36,159
I can. Who said I didn't see her?

93
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,760
Regarding the students who died at the Academy,

94
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:42,320
I heard they had conflicts with you.

95
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:45,000
It is said that you clashed multiple times at the Academy.

96
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:45,730
Is that true?

97
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,800
I didn't.

98
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,240
What? Speak up.

99
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:52,000
You were the one who made those boys at the Academy bully our Chuyi.

100
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,600
Right. Why are you even here?

101
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:56,440
Bai Manchuan, I am here to investigate on His Majesty's orders.

102
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,560
Stop getting in my way

103
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,440
and obstructing the investigation.

104
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,080
Bai Chuyi.

105
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:03,600
I heard the victims publicly humiliated you,

106
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,180
and even got physical.

107
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,320
Do you hate them?

108
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,040
No.

109
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,840
I don't hate them.

110
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,450
It really wasn't me.

111
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,800
If you are innocent,

112
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,880
why are you so nervous?

113
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:13,440
Enough.

114
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:15,720
She's just a child.

115
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,920
If you really want to investigate,

116
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,600
conduct the interrogation at the government office.

117
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,880
Why come to the House of Marquis Zhongyi to place blame?

118
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:24,360
Don't use those tactics on our Bai family.

119
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,240
Exactly.

120
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,400
If Chuyi says she didn't do it, she didn't.

121
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,680
This involves human lives.

122
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,160
Don't use that to pressure me.

123
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,400
The Third Prince also assigned me to investigate this.

124
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,520
I swear on the honor of the House of Marquis Zhongyi,

125
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,560
I will uncover the truth as soon as possible.

126
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,420
If you truly want to investigate,

127
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,520
we will cooperate.

128
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:42,640
But if you just want an excuse to harm the Bai family,

129
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,360
I will fight you to the bitter end.

130
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,050
Princess, look at them.

131
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,080
I have practiced mental arts since childhood.

132
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,940
I can sense people's intentions.

133
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,020
If she really killed someone,

134
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,080
I will be able to sense it.

135
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,280
I didn't kill anyone.

136
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,010
I didn't.

137
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,920
I didn't kill anyone.

138
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,440
I didn't kill anyone.

139
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:09,970
Chaohua.

140
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:11,890
Princess Tuoya.

141
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,480
Stop bullying Chuyi.

142
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,080
Chuyi.

143
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,080
Are you okay?

144
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,560
Stop bullying Chuyi.

145
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,360
You people...

146
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,160
I don't want to repeat myself.

147
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,680
I won't say it a second time.

148
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:23,520
No one can touch the Bai family in my presence.

149
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,240
Aren't you leaving?

150
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,960
If you don't go, I'll tell on you.

151
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:27,800
Everyone knows,

152
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,880
my father is very protective.

153
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,740
Your Highness.

154
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,130
Let's go for now.

155
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:35,800
Chuyi.

156
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,130
Chuyi, don't be afraid.

157
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:37,880
We are all here.

158
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:38,810
Sister-in-law.

159
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:41,320
Did I bring trouble to the Manor again?

160
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,960
You are a Bai.

161
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,760
We'll handle whatever happens.

162
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,480
Chuyi.

163
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,960
Chaohua and Adai are looking after her.

164
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,760
The doctor has seen her.

165
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,040
He said Chuyi is fine.

166
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,560
Don't worry too much.

167
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:58,040
By the way, what did you want to tell me in the woods?

168
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,960
I once heard at the border...

169
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,160
there is a soul-stealing secret art.

170
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,520
It is unique to the Yueshi Kingdom.

171
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,960
I also wanted to tell you...

172
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,720
I smelled a scent in the woods.

173
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,400
What scent?

174
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:12,840
Blood mixed with herbs and animal fat.

175
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,480
And a faint smell of incense ash.

176
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,640
It was very familiar.

177
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:21,000
It's the smell from the gambling house.

178
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,960
To be precise,

179
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:24,000
it's the scent on Ji Ruyu.

180
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,920
Are you sure?

181
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,650
I've trained my nose for years.

182
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,210
I can't be wrong.

183
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,679
That day, I also felt someone watching us.

184
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,960
Considering Tuoya's behavior,

185
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,799
the person Wuyue said was watching Chuyi...

186
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,400
is Tuoya.

187
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,400
But...

188
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:46,080
what is her goal?

189
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,400
We need more evidence.

190
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:50,960
Father.

191
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,520
Qiangwei.

192
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,360
The sky of Dasheng...

193
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,880
is due for a change.

194
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,560
You called me back...

195
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:02,280
just to tell me this treasonous idea?

196
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,600
My good daughter.

197
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,080
I know you've been wronged.

198
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,580
When I take the throne,

199
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,380
I will make it up to you double.

200
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,480
You are the Prime Minister.

201
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,000
A subject meant to serve the ruler.

202
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,960
How dare you?

203
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,480
Qiangwei.

204
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,480
Listen to me. Just put your mind at ease.

205
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,800
You want me to watch you usurp the throne?

206
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,330
And you tell me to be at ease?

207
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,920
Have you been infected by that madman Shen Lingbo?

208
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,200
I am not mad.

209
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:40,000
I'm doing this for your own good.

210
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,000
Stop talking.

211
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,320
I don't want to hear anymore.

212
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,040
The Emperor is critically ill.

213
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,760
The court is in utter chaos.

214
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,360
If we don't act,

215
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,480
we will be purged by others.

216
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,130
You want to harm him.

217
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,580
Then why did you make me marry him?

218
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,840
Have you ever thought about...

219
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,680
what will happen to me?

220
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,960
You just need to cooperate with me.

221
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,400
When I ascend the throne,

222
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,400
you will be second only to one...

223
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,680
and above all others.

224
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,720
What is this?

225
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:18,840
Just put a few drops in the Emperor's morning tea.

226
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,930
Within ten days,

227
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:22,040
the Emperor will fall gravely ill.

228
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:24,240
No! I won't kill anyone.

229
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:27,280
You have the easiest access in the palace.

230
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,240
His Majesty favors you the most.

231
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,640
You are the perfect person to do it.

232
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,440
If you want to rebel, do it yourself.

233
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,680
I won't kill anyone.

234
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,320
You are my daughter.

235
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:41,720
You said you would give everything for our family.

236
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,080
I did say that.

237
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,240
But I never said I would help you kill.

238
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,440
And I certainly never said I would help you assassinate the Emperor.

239
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:47,960
Stop!

240
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,370
If you don't do this,

241
00:10:57,760 --> 00:11:00,560
the Emperor will find out about me sooner or later.

242
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:03,760
Then you will have nothing left.

243
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,220
If you back out now,

244
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,960
you are pushing the Shen family into a fire pit.

245
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,520
Qiangwei.

246
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,780
For the Shen family...

247
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,480
What a great excuse.
